\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3}{\ignorespaces Unified cross-domain text-to-audio generation and evaluation pipeline. The top row carries the generation flow (prompt enrichment $\to $ CLAP encoding $\to $ latent diffusion / TTS $\to $ waveform synthesis), while the bottom row implements the intent-alignment evaluation flow (CLAP audio encoding $\to $ GIAF metrics). The decoupled architecture ensures evaluation is independent of the generative backbone.\relax }}{4}{figure.caption.3}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:pipeline}{{3}{4}{Unified cross-domain text-to-audio generation and evaluation pipeline. The top row carries the generation flow (prompt enrichment $\to $ CLAP encoding $\to $ latent diffusion / TTS $\to $ waveform synthesis), while the bottom row implements the intent-alignment evaluation flow (CLAP audio encoding $\to $ GIAF metrics). The decoupled architecture ensures evaluation is independent of the generative backbone.\relax }{figure.caption.3}{}}
